                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The scheme \"Assistance for Area Expansion of Vegetable Crops through Hybrid Seed\" by the Agriculture and Co-operation Department, Government of Gujarat, aims to support vegetable farmers in enhancing their cultivation areas using hybrid seeds and to promote natural farming practices. The financial assistance provided under the scheme helps reduce input costs and encourages environmentally sustainable agricultural methods among the farming community."
